# app/ is the built frontend the server serves at :3001. There is NO build step at
# deploy time — the phone loads whatever app/ is committed — so the bundle MUST be
# tracked. vite emits new content-hashed filenames each build, so the whole dir stays
# tracked: after any src/*.tsx|*.css change, run `npx vite build` and commit app/.
